{"tid":1452362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全港最大流動文宣平台上線啦！","createTime":"2019-08-12T01:01:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T07:28:00.000Z","uid":278288,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b8011e8ec02566d1ccfa22e8d4c5b9814de26e5e","tid":1452362,"uid":278288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:01:12.000Z","msg":"嗰個就係你自己！<br />\n<br />\n請各位手足save低最震撼嘅影片同錄音<br />\n喺等車搭1車期間播放<br />\n錄音例如晴朗嘅分享，影片例如義士被按頭磨地<br />\n錄音最好簡潔易明，片段最好夠暴力，唔好玩曲線<br />\n有ipad或大mon機最好放喺頭頂等人睇到<br />\n<br />\n我最怕唔係香港人欠缺良知，係香港人嘅善忘<br />\n我地要香港人時刻記住中共、港共、黑警所對我地做成嘅一切暴行<br />\n我地要真正打破同溫層以外人士嘅交流<br />\n<br />\n因為你係和平使者，<br />\n你唔敢企前綫<br />\n因為你要養家，<br />\n你唔敢罷工<br />\n因為你怕熱怕曬，<br />\n你唔敢出嚟集會遊行<br />\n<br />\n唔行出嚟嘅原因有千百種<br />\n請問你係咪連播條片嘅勇氣都冇？"},{"pid":"4738df5b534b3b876b115c067403344209666b39","tid":1452362,"uid":51641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:08:59.000Z","msg":"搭車airdrop 等lift airdrop"},{"pid":"2352344dfb1826fb3eb412d8fad1c053d761b332","tid":1452362,"uid":278288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:16:11.000Z","msg":"零成本嘅嘢，你肯唔肯做？"},{"pid":"329104fde04f559e749c6e0e6c8f5446134f8eac","tid":1452362,"uid":278288,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:23:49.000Z","msg":"自推 1"},{"pid":"d741c83e00877b413f807bf4b0b3f4e7abb5e9d1","tid":1452362,"uid":278288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:44:27.000Z","msg":"自推 2"},{"pid":"f00c38abc3c0db76c1a7f9ace3e4b23c26bfabf3","tid":1452362,"uid":278288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:00:11.000Z","msg":"自推 3"},{"pid":"ffaa0e6bcc0f586fb86136c915f26602106dd869","tid":1452362,"uid":278288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:05:49.000Z","msg":"自推 4"},{"pid":"f5664faa13f8f53e630b1aaecac1d9602263f243","tid":1452362,"uid":50414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:06:52.000Z","msg":"推"